Please be aware this spec file is based on the original spec file that nginx provides in their source rpm packages.

Run the below commands to build:

stable: (ulyaoth-nginx)
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-nginx/build-nginx.sh ; chmod +x build-nginx.sh ; ./build-nginx.sh

mainline: (ulyaoth-nginx-mainline)
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-nginx/build-nginx-mainline.sh ; chmod +x build-nginx-mainline.sh ; ./build-nginx-mainline.sh

ulyaoth-nginx-mainline-selinux:
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-nginx/build-nginx-mainline-selinux.sh ; chmod +x build-nginx-mainline-selinux.sh ; ./build-nginx-mainline-selinux.sh
